{"tid":2218094,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"琴日咁多人問我幾時出兵？而家答你。","createTime":"2020-09-26T03:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T06:42:34.000Z","uid":56428,"like":10,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"11006d74c0e35c6908026ec9d83f7bd9fc962efb","tid":2218094,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T03:20:28.000Z","msg":"我屌曬你班鍵盤佬啦。 上年721開始好多義教gp。過左一個月唔洗己經無乜人join。<br />\n全民上街 ，上條撚呀。 我俾你聽日 有廿萬人出黎都係廢既，因為大家呢一年都無鍛鍊過自己，出到街咪又係俾警犬禁撚住打。 <br />\n<br />\n如果你認為體能係打唔贏槍炮，去同美軍講啦。 問佢地點解有體能訓練。 <br />\n因為香港無強制軍訓無預備役，普通市民根本無服從性 戰術訓練，所以面對有操練過既部隊 我哋更加需要訓練體能、學習組織力。 <br />\n<br />\n預期大家繼續喊苦喊忽，但連基本體能都收皮既。 無謂抗爭 無謂國際遊說，因為你永世都俾人睇唔起。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上對話只係針對 懶鬼 港豬。  <br />\n<br />\n如果大家再有義教gp 留言分享<br />\n<strong>telegram:</strong><br />\n@TunYuanTianFightingSchool<br />\n@ekrtc<br />\n@ekrtc_bot<br />\n@cometrainwithus<br />\n @YLSTC<br />\n @Hkersgym"},{"pid":"a5ad3c0fd99f9aa9fbddaaf5ee90f27af2f2d043","tid":2218094,"uid":56428,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T03:47:18.000Z","msg":"無做運動都懶。 笑死。 負評就走。"},{"pid":"0f407822afcd4241661a9612d9eed5a36a561f61","tid":2218094,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:15:36.000Z","msg":"講得啱"},{"pid":"92274e5aef87ea4e123a020192de62affbb78a97","tid":2218094,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T05:26:51.000Z","msg":"東亞病夫"},{"pid":"16173b429cc06a71f2bcd9fdfcfec9c2a0bad2b5","tid":2218094,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:12:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e9f5c9ed0e858014a11b2ab555b051be50aaeda","tid":2218094,"uid":32667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:14:48.000Z","msg":"連登講真話小心會比人話五毛PR，無事我去返工了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d689f147191f54c517ee16aa4396043b90d2951a","tid":2218094,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-